### Recommended Actions

{% if risk_score == "critical" %}
1. Escalate to senior legal counsel immediately.
2. Do not send any response to the counterparty without sign-off.
3. Consider requesting a call to negotiate the flagged terms before
   accepting any markup.
{% elif risk_score == "high" %}
1. Legal review required for all high-risk clauses before counter-offer.
2. Prepare position paper for negotiation.
{% elif risk_score == "medium" %}
1. Review flagged clauses and determine acceptable compromises.
2. Standard counter-redline process applies.
{% else %}
1. Minor edits — standard legal review is sufficient.
2. Counter-offer or acceptance at legal team's discretion.
{% endif %}

